{"tid":2462082,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟講兩句 想時間快啲過 (63)","createTime":"2021-03-25T18:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T19:04:21.000Z","uid":304074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"044ac9f4d4de5488f111a5e5426125353fa2ff15","tid":2462082,"uid":304074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:48:45.000Z","msg":"依個post係俾失眠 失戀 想吐苦水 傾心事嘅人圍爐<br />\n<br />\n多謝上幾個post陪過我 俾過意見我嘅咁多位！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依個post 除咗係圍爐取暖 <br />\n大家都可以入嚟吹下水 發下癲<br />\n分享一下去嗰邊 做咗啲乜嘢 <br />\n除咗擺低自己心事 都可以散播正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩開心野想分享都可以返嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKai子！窮！雪！多疑絲！ 大粒麥！跟我來巴！<br />\nCylmomt！辣油！可能巴！塵埃！Gary！<br />\n戒賭！宋文德！唔好玩絲！擱淺絲！成熟巴！<br />\n旅行巴！因緣巴！洞洞丸！別姫！茄豆！金太！<br />\n獵豹絲！毒計巴！離巴！喬！<br />\n已讀！中薯！PHY！本澤馬！貓狗！<br />\n雪花非花！風絲！教授！<br />\n仲有好多位！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗚 越來越多人唔係記得好清楚<br />\n如果你成日留名 但係我唔記得加你個名嘅話對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隨便插嘴is okay<br />\n依度無規矩的 free~<br />\n當然發表意見要考慮對方感受啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95c5e5cd1b4fe9dd855f0a6605b03a1b88c3218","tid":2462082,"uid":326957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:48:55.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"4f107247c0677d4f488432b3594a476d83c736c7","tid":2462082,"uid":59767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20e7408f13666c8045d6175bab1751b643d64c7","tid":2462082,"uid":59767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9